    Continent
    This class maintains all the data members and methods related to each continent.

    Country
    This class maintains all the data members and methods related to each country.
    CountryTest
    It contains different Junit tests for the methods defined in Country
    Database
    This is a Database that holds the continent details, and player details This has singleton implementation so that the list of continent/player is not duplicated in a single game run
    GamePlay
    This Class maintains the state of the game and current player.
    GamePlayTest
    It contains different Junit tests for the methods defined in GamePlay
    Graph
    This class creates the graph of the game.
    Mapx
    This file holds most of the logic of the game
    MapxTest
    It contains different Junit tests for the methods defined in Mapx
    Player
    This file holds data members and all the methods which are related to player.
    PlayerTest
    It contains different Junit tests for the methods defined in Player
    TestSuite
    This is a Junit testsuite that is used to run the tests defined in: ContinentTest, CountryTest, PlayerTest, MapxTest, GamePlayTest
